{"tid":128616,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Starbucks 員工的心底話　最怕客人講「Large」","createTime":"2017-02-21T03:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T15:28:19.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2413df98de24440d8be67d345e796c2d67f49572","tid":128616,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"中環人返工前去 Starbucks 買咖啡叉電，似是必然之事。但在美國 Starbucks 當咖啡師的 Brian Beckwith ，早前在 Travel + Leisure 撰文寫了顧客做的最差事情，盤點一下看你有沒有做過？<br />\n<br />\n1. 沒講明咖啡Size<br />\n<br />\n上班族返工前像喪屍，但也要清楚你要的是甚麼Size。眾所周知， Starbucks 用的是Tall、 Grande和 Venti，但 Brian 說有 3 份一人分不清想要的 Size，顧客說「Large」而員工不知你點的是甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n2.  點飲品時別講電話<br />\n<br />\n請花幾秒時間跟員工點咖啡，別邊點邊傾電話/ 玩 WhatsApp，不單沒禮貌還可能落錯單，並躭誤輪候的人流。<br />\n<br />\n3. 將咖啡倒掉<br />\n<br />\n若你預了要加忌廉 / 奶在咖啡內，請盡早揚聲，否則員工會將小半杯咖啡倒掉，以騰出容量放忌廉，做成浪費。<br />\n<br />\n4. 勿點後「加冰」<br />\n<br />\n跟港式茶餐廳一樣，若光叫「咖啡」就是熱咖啡，但奇怪的是 espresso 也有人叫凍的，倘若真要凍咖啡，也請早揚聲，以免重新再做影響工作流程。<br />\n<br />\n5. 別焦急Order逐個來<br />\n<br />\n你剛點了一杯小號咖啡，員工會按 Order 製作，別指望你可比別人先拿，最沒禮貌的是問咖啡師可否先做，他們沒這個責任。"},{"pid":"4c7fa1778fe5ab2961877222bc35f8c989319cf7","tid":128616,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"香港人咁低質真係冇乜資格享受好似Starbucks咁優秀既咖啡店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae65496defed0f4e0c5cd1a8742426078c853dda","tid":128616,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人咁低質真係冇乜資格享受好似Starbucks咁優秀既咖啡店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes"},{"pid":"5ba9c1502f915439dfecbc9049edfa6a9c4f4c28","tid":128616,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人咁低質真係冇乜資格享受好似Starbucks咁優秀既咖啡店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyes</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83e408bd9507128cb047b13afc9e18c93d57cd2","tid":128616,"uid":52003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"又貴又唔好飲,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa116d0c303bdeba2212e8f81ac5d85ced3a841","tid":128616,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"識飲一定係飲large iced espresso 奶後加"},{"pid":"4700e7a9419acb5622af2857396d7538e622b0f3","tid":128616,"uid":67116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔用small medium large 多舊魚"},{"pid":"e98e4077ee413c9d158ef289e77399d7e7ee637c","tid":128616,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"講開最大個隻size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b968bf58f9a98a424beab01f1e6ef9b24fab11f","tid":128616,"uid":83610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又貴又唔好飲,不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2421ba412363eb8755995f5ed17fc08ba36a4f4b","tid":128616,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"叫開venti<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry"},{"pid":"ccc5ffe640a0ccc4a7915c42c49cf07e2ec0b2bc","tid":128616,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"The largest one please"},{"pid":"7cf3cdc07bb05b70fe14ed820efdbd001e4a5248","tid":128616,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fecbadbb59bf167da1b6dc050d92dd75de700ce8","tid":128616,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔用small medium large 多舊魚</blockquote><br />\n都唔明點解唔用通用字眼<br />\n係要用特別字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b4534c601c3e20d23d00acd835bdcbb90fa3ff","tid":128616,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"I get it, you&rsquo;re at Starbucks because you need your daily fix of caffeine, and if you&rsquo;re anything like me, you&rsquo;re like a zombie before you get it. With that being said, though,<span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">more people than you would think don&rsquo;t say what size drink they want &mdash; probably about a third of all customers don&rsquo;t.<br />\n有多到你唔信既奧客，有幾多？大概三分之一都唔記得講要咩size<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Even if you don&rsquo;t know the Starbucks lingo, you can ask for a &ldquo;large&rdquo; and we&rsquo;ll know what it means<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔識Starbucks ge術語，你直接講Large我地都會明<br />\n</span>, </span><br />\n<br />\nbut, please, don&rsquo;t give us some really complicated order without saying what size so we can actually mark the cup as you say it. It just gets really repetitive having to ask customer after customer what size drink they want while trying to remember their orders.<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/spoonuniversity.com/lifestyle/starbucks-worst-things-you-can-do/amp?client=safari\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.uk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fspoonuniversity.com%2Flifestyle%2Fstarbucks-worst-things-you-can-do%2Famp%3Fclient%3Dsafari&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=933e1927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/spoonuniversity.com/lifestyle/starbucks-worst-things-you-can-do/amp?client=safari</a><br />\n<br />\n屌，邊度黎條on9仔亂咁譯譁眾取寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfba3cc2fab2677bf5ab80760c6c438d93827813","tid":128616,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"叫開那提"},{"pid":"758fd6df075834cdac505ca251a85ffae02cee3e","tid":128616,"uid":9252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"我講large 有咩撚問題啊， 美國發跡，唔撚用英文"},{"pid":"16fd585b39442f66ca6c99aae2ababe8512af3f0","tid":128616,"uid":17546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"用開中文叫  我比錢點解要我就佢講英文"},{"pid":"679607cd7300a6db747b2365209e5387893a066c","tid":128616,"uid":11979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/21/144353_09f1dba518504a622811fcb905e863dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F144353_09f1dba518504a622811fcb905e863dc.jpg&h=5367a663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錯野唔想跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f415a6b5917aa5d2b871bd6c3219d8a051dabae2","tid":128616,"uid":31545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"叫開grenade"},{"pid":"f2e95721c7e0e989a79f92f589f1d1fd451ca32e","tid":128616,"uid":29001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫開grenade</blockquote><br />\n不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaf489221f2e99989847e955816cacdf04261c5","tid":128616,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/